w Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-latin; mso-bidi-theme-font: major-latin; color: black; mso-fareast-language: VI;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"mso-tab-count: 1;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>2. Biểu hiện của bệnh:</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"VI\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-latin; mso-bidi-theme-font: major-latin; color: black; mso-fareast-language: VI;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"mso-tab-count: 1;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>+ Thay đổi bất thường v&agrave; k&eacute;o d&agrave;i về th&oacute;i quen đi cầu như ti&ecirc;u chảy, t&aacute;o b&oacute;n.<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"mso-tab-count: 1;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>+ Cảm gi&aacute;c muốn đi cầu m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng đi được.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"VI\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-latin; mso-bidi-theme-font: major-latin; color: black; mso-fareast-language: VI;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"mso-tab-count: 1;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>+ Ph&acirc;n c&oacute; m&agrave;u đỏ hay sẫm mầu.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"VI\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-latin; mso-bidi-theme-font: major-latin; color: black; mso-fareast-language: VI;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"mso-tab-count: 1;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>+ Đau chướng bụng.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"VI\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-latin; mso-bidi-theme-font: major-latin; color: black; mso-fareast-language: VI;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"mso-tab-count: 1;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>+ Suy nhược v&agrave; mệt mỏi.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"VI\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-latin; mso-bidi-theme-font: major-latin; color: black; mso-fareast-language: VI;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"mso-tab-count: 1;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>+ Thiếu m&aacute;u.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"VI\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-latin; mso-bidi-theme-font: major-latin; color: black; mso-fareast-language: VI;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<span style=\"mso-tab-count: 1;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>+ Giảm c&acirc;n ngo&agrave;i &yacute; muốn.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 36.0pt; line-height: normal;\"><strong><span lang=\"VI\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 9.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-latin; mso-hansi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-theme-font: major-latin; color: black; background: white;\">3. Dự phòng ung thư đại trực tràng</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 36.0pt; line-height: normal;\"><span lang=\"VI\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-latin; mso-bidi-theme-font: major-latin; color: black; background: white;\">Các biện ph&aacute;p s&agrave;ng lọc ung thư đại trực tràng có ý nghĩa quan trọng gi&uacute;p giảm nguy cơ mắc b&ecirc;̣nh, chẩn đo&aacute;n khi b&ecirc;̣nh c&ograve;n ở giai đoạn sớm giúp điều trị hi&ecirc;̣u quả, giảm tỷ l&ecirc;̣ t&aacute;i ph&aacute;t v&agrave; tử vong cho người b&ecirc;̣nh.</span><span lang=\"VI\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-latin; mso-bidi-theme-font: major-latin; color: black; mso-fareast-language: VI;\">&nbsp;Trong số c&aacute;c biện ph&aacute;p kh&aacute;m s&agrave;ng lọc ung thư đại trực tr&agrave;ng c&oacute; biện ph&aacute;p x&eacute;t nghiệm t&igrave;m m&aacute;u ẩn trong ph&acirc;n l&agrave; x&eacute;t nghiệm đơn giản, dễ l&agrave;m</span> <span lang=\"VI\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-latin; mso-bidi-theme-font: major-latin; color: #333333; background: white;\">để t&igrave;m m&aacute;u ẩn trong ph&acirc;n m&agrave; mắt thường kh&ocirc;ng nh&igrave;n thấy</span><span lang=\"VI\" style=\"font-size: 14.0pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\',\'serif\'; mso-ascii-theme-font: major-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-theme-font: major-latin; mso-bidi-theme-font: major-latin; color: black; mso-fareast-language: VI;\">. Hơn nữa, với biện ph&aacute;p n&